ame><name><surname>Hieter</surname><given-names>P.</given-names></name></person-group><year>2005</year><article-title>The kinetochore and cancer: what's the connection?</article-title><source>Curr. Opin. Cell Biol.</source><volume>17</volume>:<fpage>576</fpage>&#x02013;<lpage>582</lpage><pub-id pub-id-type="pmid">16233975</pub-id></mixed-citation></ref></ref-list></back></article>